Package ai.agents

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BanditAgent
    Handles the bandit removing process for the ai.
    CardAgent
    Tracks all cards, and what strategy to use when having the cards, or seeing the cards getting purchased.
    CornerAgent
    Calculates the advantage of occupying the corner, by taking into account what the surrounding fields, their dice index is, and connected edges.
    OpponentAgent
    Tracks other opponents resources/cards.
    ResourceAgent
    Tracks own resources and sees what AI can purchase at any given time.
    StreetSet  
    TestTrade  
    TradeAgent
    Handles the trading process for the ai.
